        <comment xml:lang="en">Main raw material for the production of light olefins. According to the operating rates of methanol-to- and coal-to-olefins plants in China, 60% of capacity is covered by coal-based methanol, according to https://infogram.com/methanol_asia_ctotable_october22-1ho16vod7o5yx4n, accessed 15-09-2023. The remaining 40% is covered by the methanol market.


